Description_lang: The Aegis of Aggramar protects all allies within its radius by reducing damage received by $s1% but also reduces damage inflicted by $s2% and healing done by $s3%.Getting hit by Felsoul Cleave or standing within the Aegis' protection drains the shield over time.
AuraDescription_lang: Damage taken reduced by $s1%.Damage inflicted reduced by $s2%.Healing done reduced by $s3%.
